metadata.name: Napoleon's Playlist
metadata.description:
“I love power like a musician loves music" - Napoléon Bonaparte  
Napoleon Bonaparte (1769-1821) was passionate about music. Napoleon had received some rudimentary musical instructions in his youth

And now using a Time Machine he's in the present and is listening to his favourite tracks. He has a good playlist on Spotify which includes Mozart and Beethoven.

For "Strange History" Foundation World curated by @Historic_Crypto  
Midjourney (AI) + Photoshop
